## Empty

---



[Item Condition Type](https://origins.readthedocs.io/en/latest/types/item_condition_types/empty)

Checks if there is no item.

Type ID: `origins:empty`




---

### Examples

```json
"item_condition": {
    "type": "origins:empty"
}
```
